mysql> SELECT department_id, COUNT(*) AS total_doctors
    -> FROM doctors
    -> GROUP BY department_id;
+---------------+---------------+
| department_id | total_doctors |
+---------------+---------------+
|             1 |             3 |
|             2 |             2 |
|             3 |             1 |
+---------------+---------------+
3 rows in set (0.01 sec)

