mysql> SELECT room_type, COUNT(*) AS available_rooms
    -> FROM rooms
    -> WHERE status = 'Available'
    -> GROUP BY room_type
    -> HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
+--------------+-----------------+
| room_type    | available_rooms |
+--------------+-----------------+
| General Ward |               2 |
+--------------+-----------------+
1 row in set (0.01 sec)

